column1: no lie i forgot it was my moms birthday... until facebook reminded me. oops my dad spoils me 😌 sometimes i just need to escape... 😌 ugh. hang overs suck. i don't wanna work. #strugglebus i love the days i get a two hour lunch break! atlanta sucks when your bf looks good as fuck... 😏😍 i got a  ... 😉 honda was my next stop but i fell in love with this! holy fack morning traffic is awful dads out of town & i can't sleep. #great sweet baby jesus you're handsome 😏 when your ex texts you like nothing's wrong. #wehaventtalkedintwoyears #byefelicia some creepy rat bastard keeps staring at me. only 20 people left in front of me #fml i forgot how much i hate the dmv #yas helen keller jokes get funnier every time... lmao i want a bulldog so badly at the point of being hangry ready for bed. ugh at my mental capacity. ready for a nervous break down sometimes all you need is a little get away with your favorite guy... 😏 #blessed hey girl hey signed! this fucker is mine 😍 2015   corolla s premium has my name on it. 😍 i swear on my days off no one texts me, but when i'm working my phone doesn't stop. 😑 when people talk i just want to say "shut the fuck up" and walk away. got pulled over. dave is on the phone dying laughing at me. thank god the cop was cute and flirting. #notickettoday i just want a new car you're annoying me i hate ga. i'm moving to north carolina. it's currently 75° outside lol fuck new york missing you already 😌 these boys 😍 if i go crazy will you still call me superman rude boys in uniform... that will make this shitty month be better 12 hours and i will be on my way to jacksonville. blocked your dumb ass meeting today! on a scale of 1-10 im interested in him -3. i don't understand. $30 got me like 3/4 of a tank. jack this!!! this suv is way too expensive for my cheap ass. when can i have molly back 😢 oh my gosh! lol yes i'm so sore. 😣 i can't sleep. i'm in way too much pain 😢 shoot me in the face thank you! holy fuck. i hate you kidney stones too hype for jacksonville 😏 by the way - kidney stones effing suckkkk it's snowing hard in roswell!! i just want my kidneys to stop hurting this pain medicine isn't doing anything for me i'm still doubled over in pain. what the hell that sounds like a perfect night. pain meds & bed need a new victim hoped up on pain meds screw you kidney infections ugh! waking up with shooting pains in my kidneys. not how i want to start my monday obsessed high school has made me realize that you only need one best friend and like three close friends, because you realize how fake everyone is i just finished the fifty shades trilogy. in 3 days lolololol some people are worth melting for who wants normal anyways hung over + work = no bueno fifty shades of grey was a success :) i'm going to see fifty shades tonight! it's snowing!!! :) missing my favorite. ❤️ i don't wanna work today just wanna see fifty shades of grey 😟 starbucks makes me happy annnnd i'm over you. just like that 😘 anxiety at an all time high. beers with my boys flipping out right now some friends i have wtf hot bubble baths on this fine day 👍 "don't lie. you got it all figured out... that smile has got me spinnin' around" …duh date night w this cutie 😏😉❤️ 😘 don't tell me what i wanna hear. show me what i need to see you make me wanna pull this truck to the side of the road... 😏 😌 is it pathetic i miss you .... 😔 hospitals are no bueno... 😔😷 rt my boyfriend isn't allowed to watch the animal planet. he might see his ex there. gwen stefani needs to get off the strange right now i just want a tiffany's bracelet 😳😣 the thought that tomorrow is monday makes me sick miss you 😊 sometimes i think about moving home... then i get snapchats of the snow. #ilikethewarmth phone reset. 0 contacts 😢 hehe 😉 love you babes 3 words. 8 letters. say it & i'm yours today is beautiful outside! opening the windows & doors to try to get rid of my sickies if my neighbor doesn't put his maserati away and quit racing it up the road i'm gonna flip. just saying. nate archibald is beyond handsome 😍 no ragrats restarting gossip girl... ps where did you get that shirt in your ig pic ?! i'll get to looking now! wahhhhh ok fine no lol not yet yes ma'am! i'll do what i can ;-) ugh i miss you more lady :( i want to come back! i love "too soon" jokes... 😂 fuck you upper respiratory infection rt  i just want a nice looking guy that drives a huge truck & a nice beard who actually wants to spend time with me. no fucks given rt "got any plans for valentines day?" today's variety of bracelets 😍 #addicted #charmedarms lunch dates are the best. 😍 i'm just kinda over you. done. i'm hungry. bring me food "the best way to get on your feet is to get off your ass!" such a sad, sad day 😔 #rip i'm so sick i feel 100% worse than yesterday you just might be lookin for something... look at me. and i think you'll see those lonely eyes don't have to be alone tonight. all i want right now is one single daisy, a kiss on the forehead & reassurance that everything will be alright 😔 i don't wanna move to get in the shower. fackkkk i fucking hate you honey, your soul could never grow old we found love right where we are.. 😌 🙌 if you really cared about me you'd try ton communicate with me. lol quick fun fact about women ; we find out fucking everything. sore throats are yuckie :( please stop texting me. i do not want to hangout with you. i do not want to talk to you. and no i don't want to be hook up. #byefelicia so many compliments on how i look today... :) "we don't have to go home. we can lead the night on..." 😌 mind fuck of a game what a bunch of vaginas my mind is blown. oh. my. god seriously wanna see 50 shades of gray purging contacts is so needed rt listen, for a free big mac i could make up some nice shit about my mom too. this half time show is one big acid trip... #whatishappening rt missyyyyyyy oh my god my body wasnt ready!!!!
